data.description: Charming family home with plenty of room to roam! On the first floor you will have a galley kitchen with a bar to eat at, stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and hardwood floors. This home features 3 beds and 3 full baths! You will also have access to a 2-car detached garage with under finished bonus room or storage. Large patio for entertaining all your friends and family and a fenced in yard for all your furry friends! Minutes from the local schools. Home is conveniently located in the heart of the Tiger. An established neighborhood to grow a family. Short distance to lakes and downtown Clayton for dining, shopping, hiking, and swimming!
